subject: College Athletics
Basketball
lead_paragraph: Wesley Johnson had 20 points, a career-best 19 rebounds and led a 15-point second-half run that rallied No. 5 Syracuse to an 80-73 victory over Seton Hall in Newark on Tuesday night.
